text: Grassau is a market town in Traunstein in Bavaria in Germany. It is south of lake Chiemsee in the valley of the Tiroler Ache. ==Subdivisions== Grassau has the following districts of: * Grassau * Mietenkam * Rottau * Aich * Au * Brandstätt * Einöde * Fahrnpoint * Grafing * Guxhausen * Hindling * Klaus * Kucheln * Mauthäusl * Nachmühl * Nußbaum * Obermoosbach * Reifing * Reit * Strehtrumpf * Untermoosbach * Viehhausen * Weiher ==References== Category:Traunstein (district)
title: Grassau, Bavaria
